Class HdbManagerService

java.lang.Object
service.UserService
service.HdbManagerService
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAuthService, IPasswordService, IProjectView, IReportService
public class HdbManagerService extends UserService implements IProjectView, IReportService
Provides services specific to HDB Managers, handling project management, officer assignment, and application approval.
